{"tid":1361700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析] 721元朗站恐襲要負責既警隊指揮官","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T01:28:26.000Z","uid":20477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab26eb32c6b70e093e47bfbf07dfe27aa4d9d410","tid":1361700,"uid":20477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"根據政府電話簿，警務處負責元朗西鐵站警務工作既除咗元朗區，應該仲有鐵路區！<br />\n<a href=\"https://tel.directory.gov.hk/index_HKPF_CHI.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftel.directory.gov.hk%2Findex_HKPF_CHI.html&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0G6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=d4e374c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tel.directory.gov.hk/index_HKPF_CHI.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗區</span></strong>係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新界北總區總部</span></strong>轄下，轄下應該有兩個分支係關事既：<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗分區</span></strong><br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">八鄉分區</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鐵路區</span></strong>係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">東九龍總區總部</span></strong>轄下，轄下應該有三個分支係關事既：<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鐵路青衣警察控制中心</span></strong><br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大嶼山及機場線及西鐵線</span></strong><br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鐵路報案中心</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，非常「出名」既<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鐵路應變部隊</span></strong>就唔肯定係咪鐵路區轄下，因為電話簿冇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=530015670835140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D530015670835140&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0G6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=00ab818f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=530015670835140</a><br />\n<br />\n至於呢兩個總區係邊個管？大家可以睇返警務處網頁內所記錄既警隊架構<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/os_chart.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F01_about_us%2Fos_chart.html&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0G6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=21170563\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/os_chart.html</a><br />\n<br />\n至於仲有冇其他警隊部門應該負責就請大家集思廣益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>聲明：所有圖都係<span style=\"color: red;\">政府電話簿</span>既<span style=\"color: red;\">公開資料</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nRhEAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nRhEAC.png&h=5bdf83dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKkaZAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKkaZAC.png&h=7131a013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMM5OtY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMM5OtY.png&h=1260ab55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RBUGOY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RBUGOY.png&h=f0745115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJd71OY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJd71OY.png&h=12ed61d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vm3shnj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvm3shnj.png&h=609c8cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HntLOtZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHntLOtZ.png&h=53d093b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3cdfc739559c860b12c787305a273b8b8ab030e","tid":1361700,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dfa682d0bcdbc47fd5ce9b32672feb98ff9d34e8","tid":1361700,"uid":20477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-2